[SN]TITLE[SN]
Londonderry assault victim in serious condition

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 60-year-old man is in a serious condition after being found badly injured in a house in Londonderry.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police have arrested a 42-year-old man following what it described as a serious assault.
The victim was found in a property in Sperrin Park at about 08:00 BST on Sunday morning.
The PSNI has appealed for information.
